      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the balance thing but it feels like you can't really do both at the same time if the money isn't there. if you had to lean one way, which one is actually the \"responsible\" choice for a country's future? like, is it more responsible to be fiscally disciplined or to make sure people are taken care of?",
